Revision history for Perl module App::rmspaces

0.5 2017-07-23
  * Fix bug when operating on paths with target character.
  * Do not overwrite files by default.
  * New --force option to allow overwriting files.

0.4 2017-07-19
  * Fix license fields for metadata.
  * Include test suite in distribution.

0.3 2017-07-18
  * Document mass moving files feature.
  * rmspaces is now under the App::rmspaces module.

0.2 2017-07-05
  * Verbose option.

0.1 2017-07-05
  * Option to select which char be replaced.
  * Option to select which char to replace spaces.
  * Help option.
